-- British Man Wanted in South Africa Over Wife's Death Is Arrested in U.K.
-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 2010-12-08T01:19:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-08/british-man-wanted-in-south-africa-over-wife-s-death-is-arrested-in-u-k-.html
Shrien Prakash Dewani, 30, was
arrested yesterday in Bristol, England, on behalf of South
African authorities, the Metropolitan Police Service said in an
e-mailed statement. Dewani is accused of conspiring “with
others to murder Anni Dewani,” in Cape Town, the statement
said. He surrendered at a Bristol police station, it said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
